Once you've created your account, go to the "Upgrade" section to enter your redemption code.

Create your account and login today to take advantage of all the premium features!

{% include 'email/salutation.txt' %}

{% extends 'email/base.html' %}

{% block content %}
Hi {{ shortName }},<br/><br/>
Thank you for your order.<br/><br/>

License Count: <strong>{{ license_count }}</strong><br>
Cost per {{ period|capfirst }} per license: <strong>${{ license_cost }}</strong><br/><br/>

You have paid <strong>${{ total_cost }}</strong> today and have signed up for recurring billing.<br/>
We will attempt to charge your card ending in {{ last_4 }} on <strong>{{ next_charge_date }}</strong> to renew your licenses.<br/>
If you do not wish to be charged again, please contact our support department to cancel.<br/><br/>
{% endblock %}

